---
title: Chicken & Nectarine Panzanella with Mint, Zucchini, and Fresh Bocconcini
description: What’s not to like about a salad that’s equal parts bread and veggies? This panzanella is bulked up with thinly shaved zucchini, fresh bocconcini, and juicy nectarine. Unlike most salads, this one is even better made a few hours in advance. Just toss in the arugula and mint right before serving!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-nectarine-panzanella-fca75a58.jpg
